                <mxCell id="flow_desc" value="Complete Flow: 1. Client sends request to Proxy  2. Proxy forwards to Ollama  3. Ollama processes and responds  4. Proxy captures tokens from response  5. Proxy streams response back to client  6. Proxy sends tokens to Monitoring  7. Monitoring persists to JSON" style="text;html=1;fontSize=9;align=left;verticalAlign=top;rounded=1;fillColor=#F5F5F5;strokeColor=#999999;" parent="1" vertex="1">
